  <notepads>
    <notepad>
      <note>This transformation reads files from a specified directory, formats a request for GPT, and parses the result and stores the result in a table

Parameters include:
FILE_PATH_IN - Path of the input files to summarize
FILE_TYPE - Type of files to summarize, defaults to KTR
RUN_NAME - User provided name of run, if not provided defaults to YYYYMMDDHHMISS
SYSTEM - Objectives/purpose of the system, how the files are used to generate content
TOKEN - Your bearer token parameter as assigned by OpenAI. Change the default from CHANGEME.
MODEL - Which model to use, for example gpt-3.5-turbo
MAXCHARS - How many chars to limit files to before sending to model
</note>
      <xloc>112</xloc>
      <yloc>224</yloc>
      <width>838</width>
      <heigth>186</heigth>
